Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.93,0:05:40.91,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.68,0:05:46.30,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,塔基昂  给我讲故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.66,0:05:47.36,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,塔基昂？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.92,0:05:48.73,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,讲故事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:50.61,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,讲有趣的故事
